lead_paragraph: Venus Williams moved within two wins of a possible sisterly showdown with Serena in the semi-finals of the U.S. Open by beating German 26th seed Laura Siegemund to reach the fourth round on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Venus Takes Next Step to Possible Sisters Showdown at Open
